      <description><![CDATA[
<b>New:</b>
<ul>
<li>Bring back the dashboard year filter</li>
<li>Standalone settings window with live preview column</li>
</ul>
<b>Performance:</b>
<ul>
<li>Stop re-reading and re-aggregating unchanged session history on every tick — much lower CPU and memory on large histories</li>
</ul>
<b>Fixes:</b>
<ul>
<li>Open the settings window dead-center on screen</li>
<li>Never mtime-prune Hermes/Zed dbs; probe their -wal sidecars</li>
</ul>
<p>Thanks: @aiexkwan</p>
      ]]></description>
